<!-- ==================== 10-11. CI/CD ==================== -->
<h2>10. CI/CD Pipeline &amp; Deployment Flow</h2>

<h3>Environment Promotion</h3>
<pre>
  le-dev (auto)  ===&gt;  le-uat (manual)  ===&gt;  le-*-prod (approved)

  Trigger:             Trigger:                Trigger:
  git push develop     PR merge release/*      git tag v*

  Image Tag:           Image Tag:              Image Tag:
  :dev-SHA             :uat-SHA                :v1.2.3

  Approval:            Approval:               Approval:
  None (auto)          QA Sign-off             Ops Lead + CTO
</pre>

<!-- ==================== 12. SECURITY ==================== -->
<h2>12. Security Architecture</h2>
<table>
  <tr><th>Layer</th><th>Components</th><th>Status</th></tr>
  <tr><td>Network</td><td>ALB TLS 1.3, Security Groups (5), NetworkPolicy per NS, Private subnets</td><td><span class="badge-done">ACTIVE</span></td></tr>
  <tr><td>Identity</td><td>Keycloak SSO, IAM Roles, RBAC ClusterRoles, Pod Security Standards</td><td><span class="badge-done">ACTIVE</span></td></tr>
  <tr><td>Secrets</td><td>Vault per-client paths, SSH key, EKS OIDC (IRSA)</td><td><span class="badge-done">ACTIVE</span></td></tr>
  <tr><td>WAF</td><td>AWS WAF: CommonRuleSet, BadInputs, SQLi, RateLimit (2000/IP)</td><td><span class="badge-done">ACTIVE</span></td></tr>
  <tr><td>Threat Detection</td><td>AWS GuardDuty (EKS audit + runtime)</td><td><span class="badge-done">ACTIVE</span></td></tr>
  <tr><td>Audit</td><td>CloudTrail (multi-region), VPC Flow Logs, EKS Logging (all 5 types)</td><td><span class="badge-done">ACTIVE</span></td></tr>
  <tr><td>Encryption</td><td>KMS key created (EKS secrets encryption pending admin grant)</td><td><span class="badge-pending">PARTIAL</span></td></tr>
</table>

