<div class="info"><b>Cost Optimization Tips:</b>
<ul>
<li>Switch EC2s to Reserved Instances (1yr) for ~40% savings: ~$384/month</li>
<li>Consider spot instances for non-prod workloads</li>
<li>Single NAT GW saves $33/mo but loses HA</li>
<li>Hybrid nodes run on client hardware: $0 AWS compute cost</li>
</ul>
</div>

